### ============================================================
### Sales Orders V2
### Base URL: https://localhost:49609
###
### Full sales flow:
###   1. Add items to cart         (presale-v2.http)
###   2. POST /api/v2/orders       → PlaceOrder → 201 orderId
###   3. PUT  /api/v2/payments/confirm  → confirm payment (payments-v2.http)
###   4. PUT  /api/v2/orders/{id}/deliver → mark delivered (MaintenanceRole)
###   5. POST /api/v2/refunds      → request refund (refunds-v2.http)
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://localhost:49609
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
@contentType = application/json

# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@admin.com",
  "password": "Admin@1234"
}

###

# ============================================================
# ORDERS
# ============================================================

### Get all orders — paged (MaintenanceRole)
# Expected: 200 OK  →  OrderListVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders?pageSize=10&pageNo=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get all orders — search
# Expected: 200 OK
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders?search=Jan&pageSize=10&pageNo=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get paid orders only (MaintenanceRole)
# Expected: 200 OK
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders/paid?pageSize=10&pageNo=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get my orders (current user)
# Expected: 200 OK  →  List<OrderForListVm>
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get order by id
# Expected: 200 OK  →  OrderDetailsVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get order — not found
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Place order from cart
# Expected: 201 Created  →  { "orderId": <newId> }
# cartItemIds: ids returned from GET /api/v2/cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "currencyId": 1,
  "userId": "replace-with-real-user-id",
  "cartItemIds": [1, 2]
}
###

### Place order — customer not found
# Expected: 400 Bad Request  →  { "error": "Customer '99999' not found." }
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "customerId": 99999,
  "currencyId": 1,
  "userId": "replace-with-real-user-id",
  "cartItemIds": [1]
}
###

### Update order (ManagingRole)
# Expected: 200 OK
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "customerId": 1,
  "currencyId": 2
}
###

### Cancel order
# Expected: 200 OK
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Cancel order — already cancelled
# Expected: 409 Conflict  →  { "error": "Order is already cancelled." }
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Mark order as delivered (MaintenanceRole)
# Expected: 200 OK  (order must be in Paid status)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders/1/deliver
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Mark order delivered — not paid
# Expected: 409 Conflict  →  { "error": "Order has not been paid." }
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders/2/deliver
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Delete order (ManagingRole)
# Expected: 204-like OK (or 200 depending on mapping)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###
